The Federal Home Loan Bank Board(FHLBB) announced the acquisiton of South Bay Savings &amp; LoanAssociation in Gardena, Calif., By Standard Pacific Savings ofCosta Mesa, Calif.    The FHLBB said South Bay had assets of 62.5 mln dlrs andStandard Pacific had 312.8 mln dlrs in assets.    It was the fourth federally-assisted merger or acquisitionof a troubled savings institution this year, the FHLBB said. REUTER&#3;